vote.desc: Start voting poll for all members with mentioned role. Players mentioned will be removed from the vote.

voteplayers.desc: Start voting poll for players mentioned. (Shortcut: `!vp`)

wheel.desc: Choose a random player of mentioned role. Players mentioned will be removed from the wheel.

wheelplayers.desc: Choose a random player from players mentioned. (Shortcut: `!wp`)

random.desc: Get random number between 1 and number specified

pollreacts.desc: Start a poll with custom emoji reacts (Shortcut: `!pr`)

helpInfo:
`&` can be used instead of `!`
Whenever players are listed, any number of players can be mentioned.
